ation billions of years after its star became a white dwarf. [Image description: An orange gas giant planet at left, taking up about one-third of the frame, facing a star, which appears at top right as a far smaller bright dot. The planet has subtle orange cloud bands. The star illuminates the right side of the planet like the crescent of a waxing moon. Both are on the black background of space. The words “artist’s concept” are in the bottom right corner.]](https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/exoplanet-wd-1856-b-artist-s-concept.jpg?c=16x9&q=h_438,w_780,c_fill)\n  NASA/ESA/CSA/R. Crawford (STScI)](/2026/07/02/science/webb-exoplanet-dead-star)\n  [What will happen to our solar system when the sun dies? Exoplanet system may offer preview](/2026/07/02/science/webb-exoplanet-dead-star)\n* [![This image combines 678 separate images taken by NSF-DOE Vera C. Rubin Observatory in just over seven hours of observing time. Combining many images in this way clearly reveals otherwise faint or invisible details, such as the clouds of gas and dust that comprise the Trifid nebula (top right) and the Lagoon nebula, which are several thousand light-years away from Earth.](https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/nsf-doe-rubin-trifid-and-lagoon-nebulas-10k.jpg?c=16x9&q=h_438,w_780,c_fill)\n  NSF-DOE Vera C. Rubin Observatory](/2026/07/01/science/rubin-observatory-legacy-survey-space-and-time)\n  [World’s largest digital camera begins unprecedented survey of the universe](/2026/07/01/science/rubin-observatory-legacy-survey-space-and-time)\nAd Feedback\nUS Politics\n-----------\n* [![Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez, left, and Michigan Senate candidate Abdul El-Sayed.](https://media.cnn.com/api/v1/images/stellar/prod/aocelsayed.jpg?c=16x9&q=h_438,w_780,c_fill)\n  AP/Getty Images](/2026/07/02/politics/aoc-abdul-el-sayed-michigan-senate)\n  [Ocasio-Cortez endorses Abdul El-Sayed in Michigan Senate race](/2026/07/02/politics/aoc-abdul-el-sayed-michigan-senate)\n* [![The U