onger in Monaco.\n4 hrs agoEurope](/news/articles/c4gy603z2qlo)\n[![](https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260629-131846-8a2eb2c100-web-3.12.0-2/grey-placeholder.png)![A treated image of a close-up of the Statue of Liberty's face and crown](https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/be6a/live/47161e30-7627-11f1-9510-1546718f668b.jpg.webp)\nHow the American Dream has survived 250 years, but only just\n------------------------------------------------------------\nThe American Dream has persisted since the days of the Founding Fathers, but faith in the ideal is fading\n5 hrs agoBBC InDepth](/news/articles/cx2vpz2qee5o)\n[![](https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260629-131846-8a2eb2c100-web-3.12.0-2/grey-placeholder.png)![Meta's logo is displayed against pink, frosted glass. Behind the logo are the silhouettes of people. ](https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/1fe2/live/b16ef2d0-755e-11f1-bd47-e1ebd62de3b7.jpg.webp)\nInstagram running ads promoting child sexual abuse material in India, BBC finds\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nThe ads use terms including “rape” and “child video” and link to content on the messaging app Telegram.\n42 mins agoAsia](/news/articles/cvgm4e0316zo)\n[![](https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260629-131846-8a2eb2c100-web-3.12.0-2/grey-placeholder.png)![Shoko Kawata, a female mayor in a white blazer and dark blouse sits on an armchair. Her deputy in a light-coloured shirt is visible behind her.](https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/ed82/live/d39bf9a0-7628-11f1-a627-714adb4eed6e.jpg.webp)\nA mayor in Japan announced her maternity leave - and got the whole country talking\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nIn the face of criticism, Shoko Kawata, 35, says she loves her job and is proud to be taking time off to have a baby.\n7 hrs agoAsia](/news/articles/c1mykzj15xno)\n[![](https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260629-131846-8a2eb2c100-web-3.12.0-2/grey-placeholder.png)![this composite image shows taylor swift and travis kelce together and then another image shows prep and officers outside Madison Square Garden in New York. ](https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/236d/live/cc2a4710-7675-11f1-9510-1546718f668b.jpg.webp)\nTaylor Swift's rumoured wedding celebrations begin with star-studded New York event\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nActress Lena Dunham, model Gigi Hadid and longtime music collaborator Jack Antonoff were spotted in formal attire near Madison Square Garden.\n2 hrs agoUS & Canada](/news/articles/crlw1eeez19o)\n[Ebola treatments trial begins in the Democratic Republic of Congo\n-----------------------------------------------------------------](/news/articles/c75ykve4zzxo)\n['Most massive' Russian attack on Kyiv kills at least 27\n-------------------------------------------------------](/news/articles/c4gyv05gk4do)\n[Married at First Sight UK star arrested on suspicion of rape\n------------------------------------------------------------](/news/articles/cn8k774pm3jo)\n[Moment huge waterspout twirls over lake in Germany\n--------------------------------------------------](/news/videos/ckg8eld7pj7o)\n[Rare copy of US Declaration of Independence found by volunteer in UK archives\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------](/news/articles/cgrkl104ly5o)\n---\nWorld Cup 2026\n--------------\n[![](https://static.files.bbci.co.uk/bbcdotcom/web/20260629-131846-8a2eb2c100-web-3.12.0-2/grey-placeholder.png)![Goncalo Ramos and Cristiano Ronaldo celebrate](https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/480/cpsprodpb/ae09/live/83c21b60-767a-11f1-8eb3-797554696824.jpg.webp)\nPortugal beat Croatia in chaotic finish to reach last 16\n--------------------------------------------------------\nGoncalo Ramos grabs a 94th-minute winner after Cristiano Ronaldo scores his first goal 