| # | Benchmark | What it tests | Key tasks / data | Link |
|---|-----------|---------------|------------------|------|
| 1 | **Abstraction and Reasoning Corpus (ARC)** | Pure abstract pattern reasoning from 2‑D grids (objects, counting, geometry). | 50 tasks; each task is a 2‑D input‑output grid pair. | <https://openreview.net/forum?id=E8m8oySvPJ> |
| 2 | **1D‑ARC** | Same as ARC but flattened to 1‑D arrays to make it more LLM‑friendly. | 50 tasks; each task is a 1‑D array → 1‑D array. | <https://arxiv.org/abs/2305.18354> |
| 3 | **ExtremBench** | Extremal mathematical reasoning (inequalities, extrema). | 93 standardized extremal‑finding problems from Chinese Mathematical Olympiad. | <https://huggingface.co/papers/2510.12997> |
| 4 | **DMind Benchmark** | Web3‑specific reasoning (smart‑contract auditing, DeFi analytics). | 9 sub‑domains; includes knowledge retrieval + open‑ended reasoning. | <https://arxiv.org/abs/2504.16116> |
